text: Kakabadze or Kakabadse () is a Georgian surname that may refer to: * David Kakabadze, Georgian painter * Irakli Kakabadze, Georgian writer * Sargis Kakabadze, Georgian historian and philologist * Silovan Kakabadze, Georgian sculptor and teacher * Mikheil Kakabadze, Georgian geologist * Andrew Kakabadse, British professor of Georgian origin * Yolanda Kakabadse, Ecuadorian conservationist of Georgian origin == See also == * 5270 Kakabadze (1979 KR), a main-belt asteroid discovered on 1979 Category:Georgian-language surnames
title: Kakabadze
